author: Paul Smith
title: Tech's time to shine comes as rising stars fight for their lives - The Australian Financial Review
description: The demand for tech services to keep our lives moving has never been greater, but the virus creating the demand could also kill the companies we need.
content:
Editing the Technology coverage of The Australian Financial Review over the past few years has meant publishing a torrent of start-up funding round stories, which have been growing ever larger and more ambitious.
Apart from the rare and much-heralded example… [+1769 chars]
